---
title: One-Pot Tunisian-Spiced Chicken Stew with Zucchini & Fresh Parsley
description: A big bowl of stew is a comforting, craveable meal no matter the weather (or night of the week). Tonight’s light but nourishing meal is chock-full of goodness, with chunks of carrots, slices of tender zucchini, savory onion, and sautéed chicken all simmered together in a garlicky Tunisian-spiced tomato broth and showered with herbaceous fresh parsley. Get ready to spoon up this hearty, flavorful stew that’s as satisfying as it is delicious.
